name: Blue Violet - Hand Coloured Lino Print
description:
'Blue Violet' is a lino print of two birds intertwined that's been hand painted with a subtle violet colour acrylic paint. It's a signed and numbered edition of 15. This may be released as a different colour way in the future. A light blue colour edition of 25 has already sold out.

Please note that image shown is only representative of the edition - it will more than likely be a different number from the edition, than the one shown.

It's printed/painted on 20x20 cm (approx) handmade Indian paper, which is acid free and made from 100% recycled cotton rag.

These prints look nice framed in larger box frames with the deckled edges of the paper visible, although please note it's not possible for me to frame prints to ship.

Prints will be carefully packaged flat between sturdy board and sent First Class Signed For in the UK.

Every one of my prints are produced entirely by me, by hand and therefore each one when in an edition will be slightly different, with minor variations and differences due to the hand printing and colouring processes, this means that each print is truly unique.

There's more info about my work at www.chrisbourkeart.com. Any questions feel free to email me at info[at]chrisbourkeart.co.uk
